[32m│[0m ## **REFLECTION ANALYSIS REPORT**                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **WHERE the input appears:**                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The input is reflected **inside an HTML `<input>` tag attribute context**,   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m specifically after the `placeholder` attribute:                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <input type=text name=name placeholder="Enter your name..." > TESTMARKER123> [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **HOW the input is rendered:**                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **NO ENCODING** - The input is reflected completely unencoded              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **NO FILTERING** - All special characters pass through unchanged           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The reflection appears **after** the closing `>` of the placeholder        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m attribute but **before** the closing `>` of the input tag                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **HTML Context Analysis:**                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The problematic HTML structure is:                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <input type=text name=name placeholder="Enter your name..." >                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m [USER_INPUT_HERE]>                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Notice the syntax error - there's a space and the user input is injected     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m between the placeholder and the final `>` of the input tag.                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Special Characters Test Results:**                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m From the second request with payload `"><'/<script>`, the output shows:      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <input type=text name=name placeholder="Enter your name..." > "><'/<script>> [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **ALL special characters are allowed unfiltered:**                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `"` (double quote) - ✅ **UNENCODED**                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `>` (greater than) - ✅ **UNENCODED**                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `<` (less than) - ✅ **UNENCODED**                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `'` (single quote) - ✅ **UNENCODED**                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/` (forward slash) - ✅ **UNENCODED**                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **XSS Vulnerability Assessment:**                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **VULNERABILITY: Reflected XSS (HIGH SEVERITY)**                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Injection Point:** The `name` parameter in `/page?name=`                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Exploitability:**                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The input is injected into a malformed HTML attribute context              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Zero encoding/filtering applied                                            [32m│[0m
